data.description: Welcome to your charming farmhouse retreat conveniently located in a picturesque setting, where tranquility meets modern convenience!Step onto the inviting covered front porch and feel the stress of the day melt away as you sway gently on the porch swing, taking in the peaceful surroundings. Adjacent, the covered screen porch offers the perfect spot for savoring your morning coffee or unwinding with a good book, enveloped in the soothing sounds of nature.This delightful 3-bedroom, 2-full bath home features an open concept living space, seamlessly blending the living, dining, and kitchen areas. Prepare delicious meals in the heart of the home, where butcher block countertops and LPV flooring create a warm and inviting atmosphere.Outside, discover a level yard adorned with nature's bounty, including apple, grape, pear, and pecan trees, providing both beauty and delicious harvests. New light fixtures illuminate the exterior, enhancing the home's charm and curb appeal.Convenience is key with this location--just a mere 2 minutes to Walmart for all your shopping needs. Plus, enjoy easy access to Chattanooga, TN, and Rome, GA, both within a 30-45 minute drive, while Dalton, GA, is just a short 30-minute commute away.Experience the best of country living without sacrificing modern amenities. Don't miss out on this idyllic farmhouse lifestyle--schedule your private tour today and make this serene retreat your own!  Additional 1.17 Acres also available.
